data.description: Unique property with over 2 acres.  Enjoy the views from the veranda.  3000 sq ft Greenhouse barn, RV Parking with hook ups, mobile home 8X40, ADU.  16 owned solar panels, well 300ft deep. Zoned for 2 residences.  The lot has the possibility to be split with its own paved road. The interior has built in closets, a wood stove plus central heat and air conditioning. This property does have it all! A must see.
